<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▦ 01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>秋高气爽，蓝天白云出游正当时</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200903/1b3859acd4604c7d8743f62bd21a4db9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">明明都还没感受到夏天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">转眼便入了秋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都说秋高气爽</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来到木格措</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你就会知道此话假不了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200903/922784e49e5c4022aa218e9f73277725.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几番秋雨过后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">木格措的天空被洗涤得纤尘不染</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">洁白的云朵在蔚蓝的「幕布」上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">换着花样飘过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云卷云舒，仙气十足</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200903/2b5025cff6964136bc309eb57df1e2b9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">褪去盛夏的烈日</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山上的骏马四处游走</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">漫步在半山腰、游走在海子旁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">悠哉游哉，其乐无趣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200903/5899a549b9d3443683a273a25a0f143c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200903/3ee1c9309767416294c9dfdc8efeafb3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">山风啸啸，草木飘摇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">站在海拔3700余米的木格措</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有秋老虎的炎热和湿腻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也没有车水马龙的嘈杂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有的只是那份放身天地间的逍遥与自在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200903/68e2d269b1824f01a3649668a5200bc1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-right"><strong>图@Hello向阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▦ 02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>草木繁茂，斑斓秋色即将上线</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200903/1973a5c825b94ef0bea626e032a7bd23.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都说川西之美，美在秋天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">斑斓的彩林、金黄的草甸、闲适的牛羊、</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流淌的河流……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无一不是游客向往的世外桃源风光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200903/1f3de2950f6341f2aef5f1be0df4aa9b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">木格措坐落于贡嘎山脉中段</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是国家级重点风景名胜区，也是世界自然遗产提名地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">景区除了有高原湖泊、温泉雪峰、奇山异石</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">及长达8公里的千瀑珠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还有一片走不到尽头的原始森林</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200903/fdcb4aa3e4484f58be070c24268671b7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每年秋天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这些花草林木都会逐一换上新衣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红的、黄的、紫的、绿的……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">彼此在山间交错，分外多彩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200903/f3d95e9d4e93497ea057dd802eb1ee22.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">初秋的木格措，虽没有深秋的斑斓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却独有一份夏末秋初的清新与魅力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200903/5d794065a3ef4139b7ff89c5cbf3bc8e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-right"><strong>图@Hello向阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">「欲把西湖比西子，淡妆浓抹总相宜」</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">初秋的木格措正是如此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">草木渐黄，山溪潺潺</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清新自然不做作，淡淡的妆点已是最美</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200903/3e8aa35250744dcdb5ac51abd7818c31.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200903/1e17f06812a94d4d848eb58c8b5d3240.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-right"><strong>图@Hello向阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>▦ 03</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>天气路况都OK，放心前往即可</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200903/1891f8423ad7431f8e3561d8ba6cf629.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">前阵时间暴雨频繁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">很多朋友私信景区问询路况和天气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小木木可以负责任的告诉大家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>路况完全OK</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>雅康高速全程畅通无阻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>康定到景区的柏油马路也已修好</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自驾前往完全没问题</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200903/cb41358eb5944ce4a3f5fa5f96d667ba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">至于天气情况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高原地区气候多变，很难准确为大家播报</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>但一日过四季这是木格措景区的常态</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不管怎样的天气，都有别样的风景</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不要纠结是否在下雨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁也不知道雨后下一刻将会出现怎样的惊喜</p>